<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Depart from spring"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="春を発つ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="kaf"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かふ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花谱"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Crazy for you"/><amll:meta key="album" value="狂想"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPY392200802"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2026790781"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="002Hd08J1VYjfi"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="399013966"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6HPYmvawilL5qkdhs4mt1x"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1674704368"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:19.770"><div begin="17.080" end="4:19.770"><p begin="17.080" end="19.780" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.080" end="17.320">あ</span><span begin="17.320" end="17.490">れ</span><span begin="17.490" end="17.710">か</span><span begin="17.710" end="17.880">ら</span><span begin="17.880" end="18.070">ず</span><span begin="18.070" end="18.270">い</span><span begin="18.270" end="18.460">ぶ</span><span begin="18.460" end="18.630">ん</span><span begin="18.630" end="18.840">経</span><span begin="18.840" end="18.990">っ</span><span begin="18.990" end="19.270">た</span><span begin="19.270" end="19.470">な</span><span begin="19.610" end="19.780">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">自那以后 已经过了很久呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">自那以後 已經過了很久呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Thinking that a lot of time has passed since then</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그때부터 꽤 지났구나 하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me dis que beaucoup de temps a passé depuis lors</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ha pasado mucho tiempo desde entonces</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass seitdem viel Zeit vergangen ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pensando que já se passou muito tempo desde então</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Думая о том как много времени прошло с тех пор</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È passato tanto tempo da allora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Are kara zuibun tatta na to</span></p><p begin="19.980" end="24.880" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.980" end="20.330">思</span><span begin="20.330" end="20.510">い</span><span begin="20.510" end="20.860">返</span><span begin="20.860" end="21.210">す</span><span begin="21.210" end="21.510">日</span><span begin="21.510" end="21.740">々</span><span begin="21.880" end="22.040">も</span><span begin="22.760" end="23.400">何</span><span begin="23.400" end="23.610">度</span><span begin="23.760" end="23.970">目</span><span begin="24.130" end="24.650">だ</span><span begin="24.650" end="24.880">ろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如此回首往昔的日子 已是第几次了呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如此回首往昔的日子 已是第幾次了呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">How many times have I looked back on those days</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">되돌아보는 나날도 몇 번째일까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Combien de fois ai-je repensé à ces jours</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuántas veces habré recordado esos días</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zum wievielten Mal blicke ich wohl auf diese Tage zurück</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quantas vezes já vivi os dias em que relembro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Который раз я уже вспоминаю те дни</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quante volte avrò ripensato a quei giorni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omoikaesu hibi mo nandome darou</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="22.010" end="22.840"><span begin="22.010" end="22.280">(日</span><span begin="22.310" end="22.540">々</span><span begin="22.680" end="22.840">も)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些日子</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些日子</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Those days</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나날도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À ces jours</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">esos días</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese Tage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esses dias</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эти дни</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ai giorni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hibi mo</span></span></p><p begin="29.130" end="31.060" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.130" end="29.310">も</span><span begin="29.310" end="29.480">し</span><span begin="29.480" end="29.860">違</span><span begin="29.860" end="30.120">う</span><span begin="30.240" end="30.750">道</span><span begin="30.860" end="31.060">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若 走上了不同的道路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若 走上了不同的道路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What if we took a different path</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">만약 다른 길을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et si j&apos;avais pris un autre chemin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si hubiéramos tomado otro camino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was wäre wenn ich einen anderen Weg</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E se fosse um caminho diferente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А что если бы я пошла другим путём</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se avessi preso una strada diversa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Moshi chigau michi o</span></p><p begin="31.630" end="36.900" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.630" end="31.820">な</span><span begin="31.820" end="32.150">ん</span><span begin="32.150" end="32.410">て</span><span begin="32.510" end="32.690">こ</span><span begin="32.790" end="33.160">と</span><span begin="33.160" end="33.580">は</span><span begin="34.620" end="34.940">もう</span><span begin="35.100" end="35.710">今</span><span begin="35.710" end="36.520">更</span><span begin="36.630" end="36.900">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这种念头 事到如今已是多余了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這種念頭 事到如今已是多餘了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it too late to say things like that now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">같은 건 이제 와서 새삼스러운가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il est un peu tard pour penser à ce genre de choses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es demasiado tarde para pensar en eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber für so etwas ist es jetzt wohl zu spät</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pensar nisso já é tarde demais né</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Об этом уже слишком поздно говорить да</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma ormai è troppo tardi per queste cose</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nante koto wa mou imasara ka</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="33.240" end="34.960"><span begin="33.240" end="33.420">(な</span><span begin="33.420" end="33.630">ん</span><span begin="33.630" end="33.840">て</span><span begin="34.000" end="34.170">こ</span><span begin="34.230" end="34.570">と</span><span begin="34.570" end="34.960">は)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这种念头</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這種念頭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Things like that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">같은 건</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À ce genre de choses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">pensar en eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Für so etwas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pensar algo assim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О таких вещах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per queste cose</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nante koto wa</span></span></p><p begin="40.780" end="46.710" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.780" end="41.900">僕</span><span begin="41.900" end="42.100">ら</span><span begin="42.660" end="42.870">一</span><span begin="43.020" end="43.400">瞬</span><span begin="43.400" end="43.690">を</span><span begin="43.800" end="44.890">強</span><span begin="44.890" end="45.120">く</span><span begin="45.630" end="45.880">生</span><span begin="45.880" end="46.020">き</span><span begin="46.020" end="46.200">て</span><span begin="46.200" end="46.400">い</span><span begin="46.400" end="46.710">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们坚强地 活在每一个瞬间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們堅強地 活在每一個瞬間</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We are living strongly in the moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리들 일순간을 강하게 살아가고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous vivons intensément l&apos;instant présent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros vivimos cada instante con fuerza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir leben diesen einen Moment so stark</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nós vivemos intensamente um momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы изо всех сил живём этим мгновением</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi viviamo intensamente l&apos;istante</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura isshun o tsuyoku ikite iru</span></p><p begin="47.360" end="51.200" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.360" end="47.520">他</span><span begin="47.520" end="48.120">人</span><span begin="48.120" end="49.030">事</span><span begin="49.030" end="49.230">な</span><span begin="49.230" end="49.380">ん</span><span begin="49.380" end="49.620">て</span><span begin="49.620" end="49.760">馬</span><span begin="49.760" end="50.020">鹿</span><span begin="50.120" end="50.360">は</span><span begin="50.360" end="50.720">言</span><span begin="50.720" end="50.880">え</span><span begin="50.880" end="51.100">な</span><span begin="51.100" end="51.200">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无法说出 事不关己那般的蠢话</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無法說出 事不關己那般的蠢話</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t say stupid things like it&apos;s someone else&apos;s problem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">남의 일이라는 바보 같은 소리는 할 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux pas dire de bêtises comme si ça ne me concernait pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No podemos decir la tontería de que es problema de otros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann nicht töricht sagen dass es mich nichts angeht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso ser boba de dizer que é problema dos outros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Нельзя по-глупому сказать что нас это не касается</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non posso dire sciocchezze come se fosse un problema di altri</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taningoto nante baka wa ienai</span></p><p begin="52.750" end="58.640" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.750" end="53.890">選</span><span begin="53.890" end="54.050">び</span><span begin="54.590" end="54.980">放</span><span begin="54.980" end="55.370">題</span><span begin="55.370" end="55.720">の</span><span begin="55.720" end="56.840">今</span><span begin="56.840" end="57.190">を</span><span begin="57.810" end="58.270">話</span><span begin="58.270" end="58.640">そう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">来谈谈有着 无限选择的当下吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">來談談有著 無限選擇的當下吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let&apos;s talk about the present where we have endless choices</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음껏 고를 수 있는 지금을 이야기하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Parlons de ce présent où tous les choix s&apos;offrent à nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hablemos del ahora donde podemos elegir libremente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass uns über dieses Jetzt sprechen in dem wir frei wählen können</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos falar sobre o agora onde podemos escolher à vontade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давай поговорим о настоящем где у нас есть свобода выбора</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Parliamo di questo presente in cui possiamo scegliere liberamente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Erabihoudai no ima o hanasou</span></p><p begin="59.310" end="1:03.210" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.310" end="59.760">全</span><span begin="59.760" end="1:00.110">て</span><span begin="1:00.110" end="1:00.590">が</span><span begin="1:00.590" end="1:00.850">吹</span><span begin="1:00.850" end="1:00.980">き</span><span begin="1:00.980" end="1:01.250">荒</span><span begin="1:01.250" end="1:01.760">れ</span><span begin="1:01.760" end="1:03.210">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一切 都在狂风中肆虐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一切 都在狂風中肆虐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Everything blows wildly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">모든 것이 휘몰아쳐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout souffle en tempête</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Todo se agita violentamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Alles stürmt heftig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo sopra violentamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё вокруг яростно бушует</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutto soffia con violenza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Subete ga fukiareru</span></p><p begin="1:03.950" end="1:15.110" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.950" end="1:04.370">春</span><span begin="1:04.370" end="1:04.730">を</span><span begin="1:04.730" end="1:05.160">発</span><span begin="1:05.160" end="1:05.240">つ</span><span begin="1:05.500" end="1:05.730">あ</span><span begin="1:05.730" end="1:05.890">な</span><span begin="1:05.890" end="1:06.150">た</span><span begin="1:06.260" end="1:06.620">の</span><span begin="1:07.020" end="1:07.360">胸</span><span begin="1:07.360" end="1:07.710">の</span><span begin="1:07.710" end="1:08.110">鼓</span><span begin="1:08.110" end="1:08.860">動</span><span begin="1:08.860" end="1:09.230">が</span><span begin="1:09.230" end="1:09.750">ず</span><span begin="1:09.750" end="1:10.020">っ</span><span begin="1:10.020" end="1:10.300">と</span><span begin="1:10.750" end="1:11.120">止</span><span begin="1:11.120" end="1:11.490">ま</span><span begin="1:11.490" end="1:11.880">ら</span><span begin="1:11.880" end="1:12.270">ぬ</span><span begin="1:12.270" end="1:13.380">よ</span><span begin="1:13.380" end="1:13.780">う</span><span begin="1:13.780" end="1:15.110">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿从春天启程的你 胸中的悸动永远不会停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願從春天啟程的你 胸中的悸動永遠不會停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that your heartbeat never stops as you depart from spring</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">봄을 떠나는 당신의 가슴의 고동이 계속 멈추지 않기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que les battements de ton cœur qui quitte le printemps ne s&apos;arrêtent jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que los latidos de tu corazón al partir en primavera nunca se detengan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Möge dein Herzschlag beim Aufbruch aus dem Frühling niemals aufhören</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que as batidas do peito de você que parte na primavera nunca parem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть биение твоего сердца покидающего весну никогда не останавливается</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché il battito del tuo petto che parte in primavera non si fermi mai</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haru o tatsu anata no mune no kodou ga zutto tomaranu you ni</span></p><p begin="1:15.960" end="1:27.110" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.960" end="1:16.260">駆</span><span begin="1:16.260" end="1:16.410">け</span><span begin="1:16.410" end="1:17.170">足</span><span begin="1:17.490" end="1:17.710">浮</span><span begin="1:17.710" end="1:17.900">き</span><span begin="1:17.900" end="1:18.680">足</span><span begin="1:18.990" end="1:19.200">立</span><span begin="1:19.200" end="1:19.370">っ</span><span begin="1:19.370" end="1:19.760">た</span><span begin="1:19.760" end="1:20.490">僕</span><span begin="1:20.490" end="1:20.870">ら</span><span begin="1:20.870" end="1:21.070">の</span><span begin="1:21.070" end="1:22.010">歌</span><span begin="1:22.010" end="1:22.300">が</span><span begin="1:22.730" end="1:23.480">響</span><span begin="1:23.480" end="1:23.880">き</span><span begin="1:23.880" end="1:24.100">ま</span><span begin="1:24.200" end="1:24.510">す</span><span begin="1:24.990" end="1:25.400">よ</span><span begin="1:25.400" end="1:25.770">う</span><span begin="1:25.770" end="1:27.110">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿步履匆匆雀跃不已的我们 歌声能够长久回荡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願步履匆匆雀躍不已的我們 歌聲能夠長久迴盪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that the song of us running and restless echoes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뛰어가며 들뜬 우리들의 노래가 울려 퍼지기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que notre chanson empressée et fébrile résonne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que nuestra canción apresurada e inquieta resuene</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Möge unser rennendes und ruheloses Lied erklingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que a nossa música de passos apressados e inquietos ressoe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть наша торопливая и беспокойная песня звучит эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché la nostra canzone di corsa e in trepidazione risuoni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakeashi ukiashidatta bokura no uta ga hibikimasu you ni</span></p><p begin="1:27.950" end="1:33.490" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.950" end="1:28.250">ハ</span><span begin="1:28.250" end="1:28.760">ロー</span> <span begin="1:28.760" end="1:29.490">僕</span><span begin="1:29.490" end="1:29.790">ら</span><span begin="1:29.790" end="1:30.270">の</span><span begin="1:30.270" end="1:30.480">出</span><span begin="1:30.810" end="1:30.980">会</span><span begin="1:30.980" end="1:31.240">い</span><span begin="1:31.240" end="1:31.740">が</span><span begin="1:31.740" end="1:32.350">風</span><span begin="1:32.350" end="1:32.680">を</span><span begin="1:32.680" end="1:33.130">運</span><span begin="1:33.250" end="1:33.490">ぶ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哈喽 我们的相遇唤来了微风</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哈囉 我們的相遇喚來了微風</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hello our meeting carries the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안녕 우리들의 만남이 바람을 실어 와</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Hello notre rencontre apporte le vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hola nuestro encuentro trae el viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hallo unsere Begegnung bringt den Wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Olá o nosso encontro traz o vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Привет наша встреча приносит ветер</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciao il nostro incontro porta il vento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haroo bokura no deai ga kaze o hakobu</span></p><p begin="1:33.990" end="1:39.850" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.990" end="1:34.760">運</span><span begin="1:34.760" end="1:35.040">命</span><span begin="1:35.320" end="1:35.480">な</span><span begin="1:35.480" end="1:35.740">ん</span><span begin="1:35.740" end="1:36.000">て</span><span begin="1:36.110" end="1:36.540">も</span><span begin="1:36.640" end="1:36.830">の</span><span begin="1:37.360" end="1:38.120">信</span><span begin="1:38.120" end="1:38.370">じ</span><span begin="1:38.520" end="1:38.880">た</span><span begin="1:38.880" end="1:39.010">く</span><span begin="1:39.120" end="1:39.490">な</span><span begin="1:39.490" end="1:39.640">る</span><span begin="1:39.640" end="1:39.850">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让人不禁想要 去相信命运这种东西呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓人不禁想要 去相信命運這種東西呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It makes me want to believe in things like destiny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">운명 같은 걸 믿고 싶어져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça me donne envie de croire en quelque chose comme le destin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me hace querer creer en cosas como el destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das lässt mich an so etwas wie Schicksal glauben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dá vontade de acreditar em coisas como o destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Аж хочется поверить в такую вещь как судьба</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi viene voglia di credere in cose come il destino</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Unmei nante mono shinjitaku naru yo</span></p><p begin="1:53.110" end="1:55.810" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.110" end="1:53.530">転</span><span begin="1:53.530" end="1:53.750">ん</span><span begin="1:53.750" end="1:53.880">で</span><span begin="1:53.880" end="1:54.110">置</span><span begin="1:54.110" end="1:54.260">い</span><span begin="1:54.260" end="1:54.430">て</span><span begin="1:54.620" end="1:54.890">か</span><span begin="1:54.890" end="1:55.070">れ</span><span begin="1:55.260" end="1:55.380">な</span><span begin="1:55.380" end="1:55.620">が</span><span begin="1:55.620" end="1:55.810">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在跌跌撞撞 被抛下的同时</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在跌跌撞撞 被拋下的同時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">While falling and being left behind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넘어지고 남겨지면서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En trébuchant et en étant laissée derrière</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mientras tropiezas y te quedas atrás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Während du hinfällst und zurückgelassen wirst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tropeçando e sendo deixada para trás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Падая и оставаясь позади</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mentre cadiamo e veniamo lasciati indietro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koronde oitekarenagara</span></p><p begin="1:56.150" end="2:00.400" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:56.150" end="1:56.510">何</span><span begin="1:56.510" end="1:56.740">度</span><span begin="1:56.740" end="1:56.910">も</span><span begin="1:56.910" end="1:57.250">迷</span><span begin="1:57.250" end="1:57.600">う</span><span begin="1:57.600" end="1:57.920">日</span><span begin="1:57.920" end="1:58.110">々</span><span begin="1:58.280" end="1:58.430">も</span><span begin="1:58.770" end="1:59.050">あ</span><span begin="1:59.160" end="1:59.320">る</span><span begin="1:59.420" end="1:59.680">だ</span><span begin="1:59.780" end="2:00.020">ろ</span><span begin="2:00.150" end="2:00.400">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也会有无数次 感到迷茫的日子吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也會有無數次 感到迷茫的日子吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There will be days when you lose your way many times</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이고 헤매는 나날도 있겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il y aura sûrement des jours où tu te perdras encore et encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Habrá días en los que te perderás una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wird es wohl auch Tage geben an denen du dich oft verirrst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deve haver dias em que você se perde várias vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наверняка будут дни когда ты снова и снова будешь сбиваться с пути</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ci saranno giorni in cui ci smarriremo tante volte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando mo mayou hibi mo aru darou</span></p><p begin="2:05.100" end="2:09.640" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:05.100" end="2:05.370">そ</span><span begin="2:05.370" end="2:05.500">れ</span><span begin="2:05.500" end="2:05.770">で</span><span begin="2:05.770" end="2:05.890">も</span><span begin="2:06.070" end="2:06.460">忘</span><span begin="2:06.460" end="2:06.630">れ</span><span begin="2:06.630" end="2:06.840">な</span><span begin="2:06.840" end="2:07.010">い</span><span begin="2:07.010" end="2:07.260">で</span><span begin="2:07.400" end="2:07.620">ほ</span><span begin="2:07.640" end="2:08.120">しい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">尽管如此 也希望你不要忘记</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">儘管如此 也希望你不要忘記</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even so I want you not to forget</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래도 잊지 말아 줬으면 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Malgré tout j&apos;aimerais que tu n&apos;oublies pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así quiero que no lo olvides</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Trotzdem möchte ich dass du nicht vergisst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim quero que você não esqueça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но даже так прошу тебя не забывай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure vorrei che non dimenticassi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo wasurenaide hoshii</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:07.620" end="2:09.640"><span begin="2:07.620" end="2:07.990">(忘</span><span begin="2:07.990" end="2:08.100">れ</span><span begin="2:08.150" end="2:08.350">な</span><span begin="2:08.350" end="2:08.460">い</span><span begin="2:08.530" end="2:08.780">で</span><span begin="2:08.830" end="2:09.010">ほ</span><span begin="2:09.090" end="2:09.640">しい)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">希望你不要忘记</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">希望你不要忘記</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want you not to forget</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잊지 말아 줬으면 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;aimerais que tu n&apos;oublies pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero que no lo olvides</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Möchte ich dass du nicht vergisst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero que você não esqueça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Прошу тебя не забывай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Vorrei che non dimenticassi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wasurenaide hoshii</span></span></p><p begin="2:09.070" end="2:12.360" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:09.070" end="2:09.530">月</span><span begin="2:09.640" end="2:09.820">並</span><span begin="2:09.920" end="2:10.110">み</span><span begin="2:10.250" end="2:10.470">な</span><span begin="2:10.580" end="2:10.960">言</span><span begin="2:11.110" end="2:11.390">葉</span><span begin="2:11.390" end="2:11.600">だ</span><span begin="2:11.740" end="2:11.970">け</span><span begin="2:12.140" end="2:12.360">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">虽然只是些 老生常谈的话语</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">雖然只是些 老生常談的話語</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even though these are ordinary words</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진부한 말이지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce sont des mots banals mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque sean palabras comunes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es sind zwar banale Worte aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">São palavras clichês mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хоть это и банальные слова но</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono parole banali ma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsukinami na kotoba dakedo</span></p><p begin="2:16.700" end="2:19.630" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:16.700" end="2:17.890">一</span><span begin="2:17.890" end="2:18.090">人</span><span begin="2:18.500" end="2:18.640">じゃ</span><span begin="2:18.640" end="2:18.830">な</span><span begin="2:18.830" end="2:19.000">い</span><span begin="2:19.000" end="2:19.270">こ</span><span begin="2:19.270" end="2:19.630">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你并不是 孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你並不是 孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That you are not alone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">혼자가 아니라는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le fait que tu n&apos;es pas seul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que no estás a solas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass du nicht allein bist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que você não está sozinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О том что ты не одинок</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che non sei sola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hitori ja nai koto</span></p><p begin="2:19.720" end="2:27.140" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.720" end="2:20.870">言</span><span begin="2:20.870" end="2:21.110">葉</span><span begin="2:21.440" end="2:21.620">も</span><span begin="2:21.620" end="2:22.220">喜</span><span begin="2:22.220" end="2:22.400">び</span><span begin="2:22.400" end="2:22.790">も</span><span begin="2:23.310" end="2:23.750">痛</span><span begin="2:23.750" end="2:24.090">み</span><span begin="2:24.090" end="2:24.620">も</span><span begin="2:24.620" end="2:25.000">誰</span><span begin="2:25.000" end="2:25.250">か</span><span begin="2:25.250" end="2:25.390">と</span><span begin="2:25.390" end="2:25.630">分</span><span begin="2:25.630" end="2:25.770">か</span><span begin="2:25.770" end="2:25.960">ち</span><span begin="2:26.110" end="2:26.280">合</span><span begin="2:26.280" end="2:26.500">え</span><span begin="2:26.500" end="2:26.730">る</span><span begin="2:26.730" end="2:26.930">こ</span><span begin="2:26.930" end="2:27.140">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论是言语、喜悦还是痛楚 都能与某人一同分担</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論是言語、喜悅還是痛楚 都能與某人一同分擔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That you can share words joy and pain with someone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말도 기쁨도 아픔도 누군가와 나눌 수 있다는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le fait que les mots la joie et la douleur peuvent être partagés avec quelqu&apos;un</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que las palabras la alegría y el dolor se pueden compartir con alguien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass du Worte Freude und Schmerz mit jemandem teilen kannst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que palavras alegrias e dores podem ser compartilhadas com alguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О том что слова радость и боль можно разделить с кем-то</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che puoi condividere parole gioia e dolore con qualcuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotoba mo yorokobi mo itami mo dareka to wakachiaeru koto</span></p><p begin="2:28.720" end="2:39.320" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:28.720" end="2:29.760">夢</span><span begin="2:29.870" end="2:30.650">物</span><span begin="2:30.650" end="2:31.240">語</span><span begin="2:31.240" end="2:31.530">は</span><span begin="2:31.530" end="2:31.720">い</span><span begin="2:31.720" end="2:32.310">つ</span><span begin="2:32.310" end="2:32.670">だ</span><span begin="2:32.670" end="2:32.850">っ</span><span begin="2:32.850" end="2:33.080">て</span><span begin="2:33.620" end="2:34.280">現実</span><span begin="2:34.280" end="2:34.700">に</span><span begin="2:35.290" end="2:35.470">変</span><span begin="2:35.470" end="2:35.700">え</span><span begin="2:35.700" end="2:36.070">ら</span><span begin="2:36.070" end="2:36.640">れ</span><span begin="2:36.640" end="2:36.980">る</span><span begin="2:36.980" end="2:37.160">こ</span><span begin="2:37.260" end="2:37.740">と</span><span begin="2:37.740" end="2:39.320">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些梦幻的故事 无论何时都能化作现实</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些夢幻的故事 無論何時都能化作現實</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That a dream story can always be turned into reality</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꿈같은 이야기는 언제나 현실로 바꿀 수 있다는 것을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le fait qu&apos;une histoire de rêve peut toujours être changée en réalité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que los cuentos de sueños siempre se pueden convertir en realidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass Traumgeschichten immer in Realität verwandelt werden können</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que histórias de sonho podem ser transformadas em realidade a qualquer momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О том что мечты всегда можно превратить в реальность</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che le storie di sogni possono sempre essere trasformate in realtà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yumemonogatari wa itsu datte riaru ni kaerareru koto o</span></p><p begin="2:39.940" end="2:51.180" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:39.940" end="2:40.380">春</span><span begin="2:40.380" end="2:40.750">を</span><span begin="2:40.750" end="2:41.160">発</span><span begin="2:41.160" end="2:41.250">つ</span><span begin="2:41.510" end="2:41.730">あ</span><span begin="2:41.730" end="2:41.880">な</span><span begin="2:41.880" end="2:42.260">た</span><span begin="2:42.260" end="2:42.600">の</span><span begin="2:42.980" end="2:43.230">日</span><span begin="2:43.230" end="2:43.370">々</span><span begin="2:43.370" end="2:43.730">が</span><span begin="2:43.730" end="2:44.480">誰</span><span begin="2:44.480" end="2:44.900">か</span><span begin="2:44.900" end="2:45.260">に</span><span begin="2:45.260" end="2:46.030">愛</span><span begin="2:46.030" end="2:46.330">を</span><span begin="2:46.730" end="2:47.510">教</span><span begin="2:47.510" end="2:47.860">え</span><span begin="2:47.860" end="2:48.210">ま</span><span begin="2:48.210" end="2:48.520">す</span><span begin="2:48.980" end="2:49.390">よ</span><span begin="2:49.390" end="2:49.760">う</span><span begin="2:49.760" end="2:51.180">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿从春天启程的你 每一天都能教会某个人什么是爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願從春天啟程的你 每一天都能教會某個人什麼是愛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that your days teach someone love as you depart from spring</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">봄을 떠나는 당신의 나날이 누군가에게 사랑을 가르쳐주기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que tes jours en quittant le printemps enseignent l&apos;amour à quelqu&apos;un</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que tus días al partir en primavera le enseñen el amor a alguien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mögen deine Tage beim Aufbruch aus dem Frühling jemanden Liebe lehren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que os dias de você que parte na primavera ensinem o amor a alguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть твои дни покидающего весну научат кого-нибудь любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché i tuoi giorni che partono in primavera insegnino l&apos;amore a qualcuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haru o tatsu anata no hibi ga dareka ni ai o oshiemasu you ni</span></p><p begin="2:51.950" end="3:03.220" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.950" end="2:52.360">春</span><span begin="2:52.360" end="2:52.740">一</span><span begin="2:52.740" end="2:53.160">番</span><span begin="2:53.490" end="2:53.710">の</span><span begin="2:53.710" end="2:54.140">風</span><span begin="2:54.240" end="2:54.630">に</span><span begin="2:55.010" end="2:55.240">揉</span><span begin="2:55.240" end="2:55.370">ま</span><span begin="2:55.370" end="2:55.730">れ</span><span begin="2:55.730" end="2:56.500">新</span><span begin="2:56.500" end="2:56.870">た</span><span begin="2:56.870" end="2:57.230">な</span><span begin="2:57.230" end="2:58.030">愛</span><span begin="2:58.030" end="2:58.300">を</span><span begin="2:58.700" end="2:59.120">知</span><span begin="2:59.120" end="2:59.370">り</span><span begin="2:59.490" end="2:59.710">ま</span><span begin="2:59.820" end="3:00.220">す</span><span begin="3:00.220" end="3:01.380">よ</span><span begin="3:01.380" end="3:01.770">う</span><span begin="3:01.770" end="3:03.220">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿你在初春的强风中历练 能够知晓崭新的爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願你在初春的強風中歷練 能夠知曉嶄新的愛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that you know a new love buffeted by the first winds of spring</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">첫봄의 바람에 부대끼며 새로운 사랑을 알게 되기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que bousculé par le premier vent du printemps tu connaisses un nouvel amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que al mecerte en el primer viento de primavera conozcas un nuevo amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mögest du vom ersten Frühlingssturm durchgeschüttelt werden und neue Liebe kennenlernen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sendo sacudida pelo primeiro vento da primavera que você conheça um novo amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть под порывами первого весеннего ветра ты познаешь новую любовь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché sballottata dal primo vento di primavera tu conosca un nuovo amore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haruichiban no kaze ni momare aratana ai o shirimasu you ni</span></p><p begin="3:03.940" end="3:13.180" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.940" end="3:04.280">あ</span><span begin="3:04.280" end="3:04.740">な</span><span begin="3:04.740" end="3:05.040">た</span><span begin="3:05.040" end="3:05.330">が</span><span begin="3:05.330" end="3:05.760">何</span><span begin="3:05.760" end="3:06.540">者</span><span begin="3:06.540" end="3:06.860">か</span><span begin="3:06.860" end="3:07.000">あ</span><span begin="3:07.000" end="3:07.270">な</span><span begin="3:07.270" end="3:07.750">た</span><span begin="3:07.750" end="3:08.470">だ</span><span begin="3:08.470" end="3:09.230">け</span><span begin="3:09.230" end="3:09.930">が</span><span begin="3:09.930" end="3:10.560">知</span><span begin="3:10.560" end="3:10.730">っ</span><span begin="3:10.730" end="3:11.980">て</span><span begin="3:11.980" end="3:12.260">い</span><span begin="3:12.260" end="3:13.180">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你究竟是谁 只有你自己知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你究竟是誰 只有你自己知曉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Only you know who you are</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 어떤 사람인지 당신만이 알고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il n&apos;y a que toi qui sais qui tu es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo tú sabes quién eres en realidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wer du bist weißt nur du allein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quem você é apenas você sabe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лишь ты один знаешь кто ты такой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo tu sai chi sei</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga nanimono ka anata dake ga shitte iru</span></p><p begin="3:13.740" end="3:20.170" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:13.740" end="3:14.280">誰</span><span begin="3:14.280" end="3:14.890">一</span><span begin="3:14.890" end="3:15.870">人</span><span begin="3:16.580" end="3:16.750">止</span><span begin="3:16.750" end="3:17.110">め</span><span begin="3:17.110" end="3:17.340">る</span><span begin="3:17.340" end="3:17.590">こ</span><span begin="3:17.700" end="3:17.910">と</span><span begin="3:17.910" end="3:18.510">は</span><span begin="3:18.850" end="3:19.040">で</span><span begin="3:19.040" end="3:19.350">き</span><span begin="3:19.350" end="3:19.940">な</span><span begin="3:19.940" end="3:20.170">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">没有任何人 能够阻挡你的脚步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">沒有任何人 能夠阻擋你的腳步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No one can stop you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 누구도 막을 수는 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Personne ne peut t&apos;arrêter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nadie puede detenerte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Niemand kann dich aufhalten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ninguém pode te parar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И никто не в силах тебя остановить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nessuno può fermarti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Darehitori tomeru koto wa dekinai</span></p><p begin="3:21.910" end="3:32.680" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:21.910" end="3:22.400">春</span><span begin="3:22.400" end="3:22.740">を</span><span begin="3:22.740" end="3:23.260">発</span><span begin="3:23.260" end="3:23.350">つ</span><span begin="3:23.470" end="3:23.720">あ</span><span begin="3:23.720" end="3:23.900">な</span><span begin="3:23.900" end="3:24.280">た</span><span begin="3:24.280" end="3:24.780">が</span><span begin="3:25.040" end="3:25.280">い</span><span begin="3:25.280" end="3:25.430">つ</span><span begin="3:25.430" end="3:25.770">か</span><span begin="3:25.770" end="3:26.510">思</span><span begin="3:26.510" end="3:26.860">い</span><span begin="3:26.860" end="3:27.130">出</span><span begin="3:27.240" end="3:28.040">せ</span><span begin="3:28.040" end="3:28.320">る</span><span begin="3:28.760" end="3:29.080">場</span><span begin="3:29.080" end="3:29.430">所</span><span begin="3:29.540" end="3:29.770">に</span><span begin="3:29.900" end="3:30.270">な</span><span begin="3:30.270" end="3:30.490">れ</span><span begin="3:30.630" end="3:31.000">た</span><span begin="3:31.000" end="3:31.370">の</span><span begin="3:31.370" end="3:31.740">だ</span><span begin="3:31.740" end="3:31.990">ろう</span><span begin="3:32.310" end="3:32.680">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">对于从春天启程的你而言 我是否已成了某天会回想起的归宿呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對於從春天啟程的你而言 我是否已成了某天會回想起的歸宿呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As you depart from spring I wonder if I&apos;ve become a place you can look back on someday</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">봄을 떠나는 당신이 언젠가 떠올릴 수 있는 장소가 된 걸까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Suis-je devenue un endroit dont toi qui quittes le printemps pourras te souvenir un jour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me pregunto si me he convertido en un lugar que puedas recordar algún día al partir en primavera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin ich wohl zu einem Ort geworden an den du dich beim Aufbruch aus dem Frühling irgendwann erinnern kannst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Será que consegui me tornar um lugar que você que parte na primavera possa lembrar um dia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смогла ли я стать тем местом которое ты покидающий весну сможешь когда-нибудь вспомнить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi chiedo se io sia potuta diventare un luogo che tu che parti in primavera potrai un giorno ricordare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haru o tatsu anata ga itsuka omoidaseru basho ni nareta no darou ka</span></p><p begin="3:33.920" end="3:42.810" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:33.920" end="3:34.400">彷</span><span begin="3:34.400" end="3:34.770">徨</span><span begin="3:34.770" end="3:35.130">い</span><span begin="3:35.470" end="3:35.880">歩</span><span begin="3:35.880" end="3:36.040">く</span><span begin="3:36.040" end="3:36.270">あ</span><span begin="3:36.270" end="3:36.510">な</span><span begin="3:36.620" end="3:36.920">た</span><span begin="3:36.920" end="3:37.260">の</span><span begin="3:37.370" end="3:37.620">背</span><span begin="3:37.780" end="3:38.490">中</span><span begin="3:38.490" end="3:38.890">を</span><span begin="3:38.890" end="3:39.140">あ</span><span begin="3:39.250" end="3:39.490">と</span><span begin="3:39.980" end="3:40.560">何</span><span begin="3:40.560" end="3:41.120">回</span><span begin="3:41.120" end="3:41.340">押</span><span begin="3:41.340" end="3:41.500">せ</span><span begin="3:41.500" end="3:41.720">る</span><span begin="3:41.720" end="3:41.850">の</span><span begin="3:41.850" end="3:42.120">だ</span><span begin="3:42.120" end="3:42.470">ろう</span><span begin="3:42.470" end="3:42.810">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在你彷徨前行的背后 我还能推你多少次呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在你彷徨前行的背後 我還能推你多少次呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">How many more times can I push your back as you wander and walk</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">헤매며 걷는 당신의 등을 앞으로 몇 번 더 밀어줄 수 있을까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Combien de fois pourrai-je encore te pousser dans le dos alors que tu erres</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuántas veces más podré empujar tu espalda mientras caminas sin rumbo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie oft kann ich dir beim Umherwandern wohl noch den Rücken stärken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quantas vezes mais poderei empurrar as costas de você que anda vagando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько еще раз я смогу подтолкнуть тебя в спину когда ты будешь брести блуждая</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quante altre volte potrò spingere la tua schiena mentre vaghi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Samayoi aruku anata no senaka o ato nankai oseru no darou ka</span></p><p begin="3:42.980" end="3:54.910" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:42.980" end="3:43.370">春</span><span begin="3:43.370" end="3:43.640">を</span><span begin="3:44.490" end="3:44.910">発</span><span begin="3:44.910" end="3:44.990">つ</span><span begin="3:45.240" end="3:45.460">あ</span><span begin="3:45.460" end="3:45.610">な</span><span begin="3:45.610" end="3:45.870">た</span><span begin="3:45.990" end="3:46.290">の</span><span begin="3:46.560" end="3:46.950">足</span><span begin="3:46.950" end="3:47.110">が</span><span begin="3:47.110" end="3:47.360">い</span><span begin="3:47.490" end="3:47.760">つ</span><span begin="3:47.860" end="3:48.140">ま</span><span begin="3:48.250" end="3:48.620">で</span><span begin="3:48.620" end="3:48.870">も</span><span begin="3:49.000" end="3:49.760">前</span><span begin="3:49.760" end="3:50.050">を</span><span begin="3:50.510" end="3:50.840">向</span><span begin="3:50.840" end="3:51.120">き</span><span begin="3:51.230" end="3:51.570">ま</span><span begin="3:51.570" end="3:51.980">す</span><span begin="3:51.980" end="3:53.130">よ</span><span begin="3:53.130" end="3:53.520">う</span><span begin="3:53.520" end="3:54.910">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿从春天启程的你 步履永远朝着前方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願從春天啟程的你 步履永遠朝著前方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that your feet always face forward as you depart from spring</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">봄을 떠나는 당신의 발이 언제까지나 앞을 향하기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que tes pas en quittant le printemps soient toujours tournés vers l&apos;avant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que tus pasos al partir en primavera siempre apunten hacia adelante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mögen deine Füße beim Aufbruch aus dem Frühling immer nach vorn gerichtet sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que os pés de você que parte na primavera sempre apontem para frente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть твои шаги покидающего весну всегда будут направлены вперед</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché i tuoi passi che partono in primavera siano rivolti sempre in avanti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haru o tatsu anata no ashi ga itsumademo mae o mukimasu you ni</span></p><p begin="3:55.700" end="4:06.950" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:55.700" end="3:56.120">春</span><span begin="3:56.120" end="3:56.500">を</span><span begin="3:56.500" end="3:56.900">発</span><span begin="3:56.900" end="3:56.990">つ</span><span begin="3:57.230" end="3:57.470">あ</span><span begin="3:57.470" end="3:57.610">な</span><span begin="3:57.610" end="3:57.880">た</span><span begin="3:57.990" end="3:58.360">の</span><span begin="3:58.740" end="3:59.110">声</span><span begin="3:59.110" end="3:59.450">が</span><span begin="3:59.450" end="3:59.850">い</span><span begin="3:59.850" end="4:00.130">つ</span><span begin="4:00.240" end="4:00.630">ま</span><span begin="4:00.630" end="4:00.910">で</span><span begin="4:01.020" end="4:01.390">も</span><span begin="4:01.710" end="4:02.110">咲</span><span begin="4:02.110" end="4:02.480">き</span><span begin="4:02.480" end="4:03.260">誇</span><span begin="4:03.260" end="4:03.630">れ</span><span begin="4:03.630" end="4:03.960">ま</span><span begin="4:03.960" end="4:04.280">す</span><span begin="4:04.730" end="4:05.140">よ</span><span begin="4:05.140" end="4:05.510">う</span><span begin="4:05.510" end="4:06.950">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">愿从春天启程的你 声音永远灿烂绽放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">願從春天啟程的你 聲音永遠燦爛綻放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that your voice can bloom proudly forever as you depart from spring</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">봄을 떠나는 당신의 목소리가 언제까지나 흐드러지게 피어나기를</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour que ta voix en quittant le printemps puisse toujours s&apos;épanouir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que tu voz al partir en primavera florezca con orgullo para siempre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Möge deine Stimme beim Aufbruch aus dem Frühling immerzu stolz erblühen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que a voz de você que parte na primavera possa florescer para sempre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть твой голос покидающего весну всегда гордо цветет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Affinché la tua voce che parte in primavera possa sbocciare in tutto il suo splendore per sempre</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haru o tatsu anata no koe ga itsumademo sakihokoremasu you ni</span></p><p begin="4:07.710" end="4:13.320" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:07.710" end="4:08.060">ハ</span><span begin="4:08.060" end="4:08.510">ロー</span> <span begin="4:08.510" end="4:09.260">僕</span><span begin="4:09.260" end="4:09.560">ら</span><span begin="4:09.560" end="4:10.010">の</span><span begin="4:10.010" end="4:10.250">出</span><span begin="4:10.590" end="4:10.720">会</span><span begin="4:10.720" end="4:11.020">い</span><span begin="4:11.020" end="4:11.480">が</span><span begin="4:11.480" end="4:12.100">風</span><span begin="4:12.100" end="4:12.420">を</span><span begin="4:12.420" end="4:12.990">運</span><span begin="4:12.990" end="4:13.320">ぶ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哈喽 我们的相遇唤来了微风</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哈囉 我們的相遇喚來了微風</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hello our meeting carries the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">안녕 우리들의 만남이 바람을 실어 와</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Hello notre rencontre apporte le vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hola nuestro encuentro trae el viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hallo unsere Begegnung bringt den Wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Olá o nosso encontro traz o vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Привет наша встреча приносит ветер</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciao il nostro incontro porta il vento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haroo bokura no deai ga kaze o hakobu</span></p><p begin="4:13.730" end="4:19.770" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:13.730" end="4:14.520">運</span><span begin="4:14.520" end="4:14.790">命</span><span begin="4:15.140" end="4:15.280">な</span><span begin="4:15.280" end="4:15.520">ん</span><span begin="4:15.520" end="4:15.790">て</span><span begin="4:15.890" end="4:16.370">も</span><span begin="4:16.370" end="4:16.620">の</span><span begin="4:17.100" end="4:17.320">恥</span><span begin="4:17.320" end="4:17.510">ず</span><span begin="4:17.510" end="4:17.840">か</span><span begin="4:17.840" end="4:18.130">し</span><span begin="4:18.250" end="4:18.480">く</span><span begin="4:18.610" end="4:18.760">も</span><span begin="4:18.860" end="4:19.240">な</span><span begin="4:19.240" end="4:19.400">る</span><span begin="4:19.400" end="4:19.770">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">命运这种东西 提起还真让人有些害羞呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">命運這種東西 提起還真讓人有些害羞呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Things like destiny even become embarrassing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">운명 같은 거 부끄러워지기도 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelque chose comme le destin ça en devient même gênant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cosas como el destino llegan a dar vergüenza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Für so etwas wie Schicksal schämt man sich fast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dá até vergonha de coisas como o destino</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">От такой вещи как судьба даже становится неловко</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Cose come il destino mi mettono anche in imbarazzo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Unmei nante mono hazukashiku mo naru yo</span></p></div></body></tt>